room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz 1962" by Time to Escape in Atlanta
room_description: State penitentiary Alcatraz, 1962. A man named Frank Morris pulled off the impossible and successfully escaped. You've been transferred to his cell, and can't help but wonder if the he left clues behind. Can you follow in Frank's footsteps and break out before the guards come back in an hour?
